自建為國的決心和勇氣，湖南終究是沒辦法。<br />\n<br />\n談湖南建設問題，我覺得這是一個根本問題。我頗有一點意思要發表出來，乞吾三千萬同胞的聰聽，希望共起討論這一個頂有意思的大問題。今天是個發端，餘俟明日以後繼續討論。<br />\n<br />\n根據１９２０年９月３日湖南《大公報》刊印。署名毛澤東。"},{"pid":"dcc5ea680360894e0fde2a63b10240bdeae2007c","tid":2029502,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"報仇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},{"pid":"f9736e43f92e49fc2898060b36c7cae0ab96fa51","tid":2029502,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcc5ea680360894e0fde2a63b10240bdeae2007c","tid":2029502,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"報仇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再講報仇 報仇係好撚空範 直接講香港人建國"},{"pid":"8b3aaa0e97a4ae609d86ad4ab45419a7fbb2ae15","tid":2029502,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9736e43f92e49fc2898060b36c7cae0ab96fa51","tid":2029502,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcc5ea680360894e0fde2a63b10240bdeae2007c","tid":2029502,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"報仇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再講報仇 報仇係好撚空範 直接講香港人建國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"或者香港人 獨立"},{"pid":"1266ba5efffed4f549bdabad21f001f00fef7d1e","tid":2029502,"uid":263213,"li